    @Generated(value="com.genesyslab.platform.commons.protocol.generator.Generator",
           date="2024-07-23T09:22:05.894-07:00")
public abstract class RequestJoin
extends Message
    Issues a request to join a chat interaction. To connect to an existing session you have to set the correct values for SessionID and UserId.
    To create a new session, SessionID should be null and you must specify values for UserId, SecureKey, Subject, and QueueKey.
